text: Gordon Harry Bahr (May 19, 1914 – May 5, 1991) was an American football coach. He served as the head football coach at the University of Wisconsin–La Crosse in 1945. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1914 births Category:1991 deaths Category:Wisconsin–La Crosse Eagles football coaches Category:People from Sheboygan, Wisconsin Category:Players of American football from Wisconsin
